OL,3,CArsenal reach Champions League final
OL,4,Cfor first time in 20 years
OL,6,FBukayo Saka scored the decisive goal
OL,7,Fto send Arsenal to their first
OL,8,FChampions League final in 20 years
OL,9,Ffollowing a 1-0 win against Atletico
OL,10,FMadrid at the Emirates Stadium.
OL,12,FThe win came after the opening leg saw
OL,13,Fboth teams draw in Spain last week 1-
OL,14,F1, Saka's goal just before half-time
OL,15,Fsaw Arsenal win 2-1 on aggregate.
OL,17,FArsenal is now set for the final in
OL,18,FBudapest on May 30 against either
OL,19,FParis St Germain or Bayern Munich.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
