OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778069461
OL,3,CArsenal reach Champions League final
OL,4,Cfor first time in 20 years
OL,6,FTuesday's win completed a remarkable
OL,7,F24 hours for Arsenal, which has laid
OL,8,Fthe foundations for Mikel Arteta's
OL,9,Fside to now complete the greatest
OL,10,Fseason in their 140-year history.
OL,12,FManchester City's draw on Monday night
OL,13,Fagainst Everton and Arsenal's win on
OL,14,FSaturday has put the Gunners in a
OL,15,Fstrong position to win the Premier
OL,16,FLeague.
OL,18,FThey last won the Premier League in
OL,19,F2004.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
