OL,3,CArsenal reach Champions League final
OL,4,Cfor first time in 20 years
OL,6,FSaka was just four when Thierry
OL,7,FHenry's side succumbed to Barcelona in
OL,8,Fthe Stade de France in 2006.
OL,10,FDespite both sides having shots on
OL,11,Fgoal it was only Saka who could get
OL,12,Fpast the keeper on Tuesday.
OL,14,FSaka was withdrawn on 58 minutes to a
OL,15,Fstanding ovation ` as he continues to
OL,16,Fwork his way back from an Achilles
OL,17,Finjury.
